project_descr: This project supports Vanuatu efforts to maintain coverage with LLINs  the population residing in malaria endemic regions

outputs.output_descr: The project will play an essential part of the National Malaria Strategic Plan 2015-2020 by procuring and distribute LLINs, providing technical, operational and M&E support to the national Malaria Programme.
